Class Section

java.lang.Object
Node<Order>
Section
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Runnable
public class Section
extends Node<Order>
Represents a section of a warehouse. Takes orders from the input buffer and waits a random amount of time between 0 - 5 seconds before sending it to the output buffer.
Author:
Wil Simpson
